Nigerian Singer, Teni Apata has taken to her social media page to talk about cheating. The musician said ladies who are cheated on should find a better way to revenge. According to her, not only should the lady cheat back, she should cheat on him with someone who is richer than her boyfriend, including their brothers and even father. In her words: “Ladies be careful oooooo let dem not chop you like ham. If they cheat on you No tears! Wipe yourself and forge higher. Anyway if they cheat on you, carry their brother and father! DAZZALL” Check out the videos here: Anyway if they cheat on you, carry their brother and father! DAZZALL A post shared by  Teniola Apata (One take god) (@tenientertainer) on Jan 20, 2020 at 3:48am PST Source